<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="perhaps-adv">perhaps <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pə'hæps, præps/    美 /pər'hæps/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-maybe">1.★ <strong>也许；大概 (maybe)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Perhaps I’ll go to the party tonight, but I’m not sure now. 
我可能会去参加今晚的聚会，但现在还不大确定。</p></div></div>